name: CoreAPI Deployment_Approve

Description

Planet 9-Deployment Approve maintains the list of all System and routes Approval request. 

API Deployment_Approve performs the operations to receive the deployment request for approval and made a new request with the state "transfer".

Operations Performed 

Systems/List

Get all the Systems- List 

ResponseSystemsList - Definition

Deploy/List

Get all the Routes - List 

ResponseDeployList - Definition

Deploy/Get

Get the Deployed object

RequestID
ResponseGet                           

Deploy/Status

Send request for transfer/ set status to Approved

ResponseApprovalStatus
